data.description: Are you looking for a beautiful home in a great area (Western Branch) with NO HOA?? Well, This Is It! With plenty of room to spread out in this Spacious 4 Bed 2.5 Bath home, it is an exceptional opportunity to get a lot of bang for the buck with a well-maintained 2 story home in The Crossings community with top-rated schools and a neighborhood park. Central to NOB Norfolk, Portsmouth, Langley & NATO. This house has been gutted and is being rehabbed from the bones out!! A huge 4th bedroom could be used as a media room, playroom, shared bedroom, and more. The luxurious all-season sunroom overlooks the entertainment-sized deck and private, fenced backyard. Shed with built-in electricity & workbenches. Also offering a Security system, Spotless over sized 2-car garage. Book your Private Tour Today!
